H0.text: What was the first name of Queen Victoria. Victoria

H1.text: What was the first name of Queen Victoria. Alexandrina is excluded, so let's consider Adelaide

H2.text: What was the first name of Queen Victoria. Charlotte

H3.text: What was the first name of Queen Victoria. ALEXANDRINA

A4.text: She was baptised Alexandrina after one of her godparents, Tsar Alexander I of Russia, and Victoria, after her mother.

A5.text: Official documents prepared on the first day of her reign described her as Alexandrina Victoria, but the first name was withdrawn at her own wish and not used again.
